Company Description: Wendy's Is A Chain Of More Than 6,500 Hamburger Restaurants IN North America And Other International Markets. Founded IN 1969, The Chain S Restaurants Serve A Variety Of Hamburgers Made With Grilled Beef And Vegetable Toppings. Its Restaurants Also Serve Garden Salads, Grilled Chicken Sandwiches And Baked Potatoes. The Chain S Restaurants  Side Dishes Include French Fries, Chocolate Chip Cookies, Chicken Nuggets And Yogurt. Its Restaurants Also Offer Wendy S Kids  Meal. Wendy's Operates Bakeries That Supply Sandwich Buns. The Chain Additionally Participates IN Various Community Activities, Such As Animal Welfare Programs, Educational Plans And Foster Care Adoption Schemes. Wendy's Is Owned And Operated By Wendy S International.

Located IN Merrick, N.Y., Wendy S Operates As A Chain Of Fast Food Restaurants. There Are More Than 6,500 Wendy S Restaurants IN Operation Throughout The United States And IN 21 Other Countries/Territories. Its Wide Range Of Menu Features Garden Sensations Salads, Combo Choices, The Super Value Menu, Frosty Shakes And Twisted Frosty, Boneless Chicken Wings, Chicken Go Wraps And Signature Hamburger Offerings Using Beef. The Firm Is A Part Of The Wendy S/Arby S Group Inc., One Of The Largest Quick Service Restaurant Companies IN The United States.

Established IN 1969, Wendy's International Inc. Is A Chain Of Fast Food Restaurant Specializing IN The Hamburger Business. Located IN North Babylon, N.Y., It Offers A Range Of Combos, Hamburgers, Meals And Desserts. Some Of Its Flagship Products Include Old Fashioned Combos, Pair 2, Garden Sensations Salads And Frosty. The Company Engages IN Numerous Community And Environment Initiatives, Such As Wendy's Animal Welfare Program And The Wendy's High School Heisman Program. Wendy's Is A Part Of The Wendy's/Arby's Group Inc., Which Is The Nation's Third Largest Quick Service Restaurant Company Comprised Of The Wendy's And Arby's Brands. It Ranked Top IN Various Categories IN Zagat's 2010 Fast Food Survey.

Established IN 1969, Wendy's International Is One Of The Leading Restaurant Operating And Franchising Companies IN The World. The Quick Service Restaurant Offers Salads, Old Fashioned Combos/Hamburgers, Fries/Sides, Beverages And Kids Meal. It Provides An Array Of Dishes, Such As Spicy Chicken Sandwich, Honey Barbeque Boneless Wings, Baja Salad And Bacon/Cheese Potato, To Name A Few. Additionally, Wendy's International Offers Crispy Chicken Sandwich, Double Stack, Frosty Shake And Grilled Chicken Go Wrap, Among Others. It Operates More Than 6,500 Restaurants Worldwide.
